    howToPlanList: ['Yanji-centered: Use Yanji as base, explore nearby attractions and food, suitable for 2-3 days', 'Border route type: Travel along border routes connecting Tumen, Hunchun and other points', 'Combined with Route 331: Yanbian is an important part of Jilin section of Route 331', 'Seasonal: Spring for rhododendron, summer for cool weather, autumn for border colors'],
