    officialEntryBody: 'Some border ports and scenic areas in Yanbian have special entry rules and reservation requirements. When visiting border areas, familiarize yourself with relevant regulations and follow border management rules.',
    notes: 'Important Notes',
    notesList: ['Border areas require compliance with regulations; no photography of military facilities', 'Some border attractions require advance reservation and identity registration', 'Korean cuisine has unique traditions; familiarize yourself with eating customs', 'Winter border temperatures are low; dress warmly', 'Yanji city transport is convenient but attractions are scattered; rental car or chartered vehicle recommended'],
    consultEntry: 'Consultation',
    faqTitle: 'FAQ',
    faqs: [
      { q: 'What type of traveler is Yanbian best for?', a: 'Its best for travelers seeking regional culture, food, border atmosphere, and route-based experiences. Its not an attraction-hopping destination.' },
      { q: 'What is the relationship between Yanbian and Route 331?', a: 'Yanbian is an important part of Route 331 Jilin section. They can be understood together for border self-drive themes.' },
      { q: 'What should I note when visiting border areas?', a: 'Follow border management regulations, no photography of military facilities, some areas require reservation and identity verification.' },
      { q: 'What food recommendations in Yanbian?', a: 'Cold noodles, BBQ, kimchi, blood sausage, rice cake and other Korean specialties are representatives. Experience them in traditional Yanji restaurants.' },
    ],
  },
  ja: {
    eyebrow: '延辺',
    intro: '延辺は国境文化、グルメ、ルート体験为主题とした目的地に最適です。单一観光지ではなく、テーマ玩法や自驾ルートと一緒に理解するのがおすすめです。',
    whatIsThis: '延辺体験とは',
    whatIsThisBody: '延辺地域の最もユニークな価値は单一観光地ではなく、国境文化、朝鮮族民俗、グルメ体験、連続ルート感の組み合わせです。朝鮮半島国境に近く、独特な地域文化と飲食伝統があります。',
    audience: 'こんなユーザーに最適',
    audienceList: ['国境文化と民族风情に興味がある旅行者', '美食と地方特色餐饮を愛する旅行者', '自驾とルート型深度体験追求者', '331国道、国境道路と連動したいユーザー', 'コンテンツ型旅行者（撮影、ドキュメンタリー、人文探求）'],
    highlights: '見どころ',
    highlightsList: ['図們口岸：国境税関景观、対岸の都市を眺めることができる', '延吉市：延辺朝鮮族自治州都 Dey、高速道路生活と朝鲜族文化の中心', '朝鲜族民俗村：朝鲜族伝統生活様式を体験できるエリア', '金達萊花海：春季特色花木景观', '琿春防川：最東端の国境点、三개를一眼で見渡せる', '延辺グルメ：冷面、烤肉、泡菜などの朝鲜族特色料理'],
